Package: streamRmongo
Title: Access to Twitter Streaming API via R
Description: This package provides a series of functions that allow R users
    to access Twitter's filter, sample, and user streams, and to
    parse the output into data frames or mongoDB.
Version: 0.3.1
Author: Pablo Barbera <pablo.barbera@nyu.edu>
Maintainer: Pablo Barbera <pablo.barbera@nyu.edu>
Depends:
    R (>= 2.12.0),
    RCurl,
    rjson,
    ROAuth
Suggests:
    rmongodb
License: GPL-2
Collate:
    'filterStream.R'
    'parseTweets.R'
    'sampleStream.R'
    'userStream.R'
    'streamR-package.R'
    'countTweets.R'
    'topRetweets.R'
    'getTweets.R'
    'readTweets.R'
    'tweets-to-mongo.R'
